table.body-wrap 
  tbody
    tr
      td 
        p
          ' Hi
          = @account.first_name
          ',
          |
        p
          | All aboard! You've been added to the
          '
          strong = @team.name
          '
          | team.
        p 
          | We're excited to see you build meaningful relationships with great candidates in the
          '
          = @team.location.city
          '
          | area.

        p.callout
          = link_to "View the #{@team.name} Team", organization_settings_teams_url(@team.organization, @team), class: 'btn', target: '_blank'
        p Chugga chugga choo choo,
        p The ChirpyHire Team
        br
        p
          | P.S. -- 
        p 
          .ps As you hire candidates, don't hesitate to reach out to us with ChirpyHire candidate stories. We love hearing from you!
